{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-jsx","path":"/jetbrains-ideas-volta-error/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"장태근블로그"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"6cc207f9-9aca-5f53-b237-7cd7dd50656e","excerpt":"IntelliJ IDEA 2024.2가 정식으로 출시됐다. 업데이트된 여러 기능 중 'TypeScript 파일을 직접 실행 및 디버그'가 가장 흥미로웠다. 바로 업데이트하고 실행했을 때 문제가 발생했다. 문제는  환경에서만 발생했다. 해결하기 위해서는 표준  인터프리터를 사용해야 한다. 는 Package Manager 도구 중 하나다. 여러  버전을 관리…","html":"<p>IntelliJ IDEA 2024.2가 정식으로 출시됐다. 업데이트된 여러 기능 중 'TypeScript 파일을 직접 실행 및 디버그'가 가장 흥미로웠다. 바로 업데이트하고 실행했을 때 문제가 발생했다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">node:internal/modules/run_main:129\n    triggerUncaughtException<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n    ^\nError: tsx must be loaded with <span class=\"token parameter variable\">--import</span> instead of <span class=\"token parameter variable\">--loader</span>\nThe <span class=\"token parameter variable\">--loader</span> flag was deprecated <span class=\"token keyword\">in</span> Node v20.6.0 and v18.19.0</code></pre></div>\n<p>문제는 <code class=\"language-text\">Volta</code> 환경에서만 발생했다. 해결하기 위해서는 표준 <code class=\"language-text\">Node.js</code> 인터프리터를 사용해야 한다.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">Volta</code>는 Package Manager 도구 중 하나다. 여러 <code class=\"language-text\">Node.js</code> 버전을 관리할 때 유용하다. <code class=\"language-text\">Volta</code> 외에도 <code class=\"language-text\">nvm</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">fnm</code>등이 있다.\nJava에서 사용하는 <code class=\"language-text\">jenv</code>와 유사하다.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"Volta-제거하기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#Volta-%EC%A0%9C%EA%B1%B0%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"Volta 제거하기 permalink\" class=\"heading-anchor before\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M6.188 8.719c.439-.439.926-.801 1.444-1.087 2.887-1.591 6.589-.745 8.445 2.069l-2.246 2.245c-.644-1.469-2.243-2.305-3.834-1.949-.599.134-1.168.433-1.633.898l-4.304 4.306c-1.307 1.307-1.307 3.433 0 4.74 1.307 1.307 3.433 1.307 4.74 0l1.327-1.327c1.207.479 2.501.67 3.779.575l-2.929 2.929c-2.511 2.511-6.582 2.511-9.093 0s-2.511-6.582 0-9.093l4.304-4.306zm6.836-6.836l-2.929 2.929c1.277-.096 2.572.096 3.779.574l1.326-1.326c1.307-1.307 3.433-1.307 4.74 0 1.307 1.307 1.307 3.433 0 4.74l-4.305 4.305c-1.311 1.311-3.44 1.3-4.74 0-.303-.303-.564-.68-.727-1.051l-2.246 2.245c.236.358.481.667.796.982.812.812 1.846 1.417 3.036 1.704 1.542.371 3.194.166 4.613-.617.518-.286 1.005-.648 1.444-1.087l4.304-4.305c2.512-2.511 2.512-6.582.001-9.093-2.511-2.51-6.581-2.51-9.092 0z\"/></svg></a>Volta 제거하기</h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p>macOS, zsh 환경에서 진행한다.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<ol>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">rm -rf ~/.volta</code>: 바이너리를 제거한다.</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\"><span class=\"token builtin class-name\">export</span> <span class=\"token assign-left variable\">VOLTA_HOME</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"<span class=\"token environment constant\">$HOME</span>/.volta\"</span>\n<span class=\"token builtin class-name\">export</span> <span class=\"token assign-left variable\"><span class=\"token environment constant\">PATH</span></span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"<span class=\"token variable\">$VOLTA_HOME</span>/bin:<span class=\"token environment constant\">$PATH</span>\"</span></code></pre></div>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">vim ~/.zshrc</code>: 위와 같은 환경 변수를 제거한다.</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">source ~/.zshrc</code>: 설정 파일을 다시 불러온다.</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">volta -v</code>: 삭제를 확인한다.</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"기능-확인하기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EA%B8%B0%EB%8A%A5-%ED%99%95%EC%9D%B8%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"기능 확인하기 permalink\" class=\"heading-anchor before\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M6.188 8.719c.439-.439.926-.801 1.444-1.087 2.887-1.591 6.589-.745 8.445 2.069l-2.246 2.245c-.644-1.469-2.243-2.305-3.834-1.949-.599.134-1.168.433-1.633.898l-4.304 4.306c-1.307 1.307-1.307 3.433 0 4.74 1.307 1.307 3.433 1.307 4.74 0l1.327-1.327c1.207.479 2.501.67 3.779.575l-2.929 2.929c-2.511 2.511-6.582 2.511-9.093 0s-2.511-6.582 0-9.093l4.304-4.306zm6.836-6.836l-2.929 2.929c1.277-.096 2.572.096 3.779.574l1.326-1.326c1.307-1.307 3.433-1.307 4.74 0 1.307 1.307 1.307 3.433 0 4.74l-4.305 4.305c-1.311 1.311-3.44 1.3-4.74 0-.303-.303-.564-.68-.727-1.051l-2.246 2.245c.236.358.481.667.796.982.812.812 1.846 1.417 3.036 1.704 1.542.371 3.194.166 4.613-.617.518-.286 1.005-.648 1.444-1.087l4.304-4.305c2.512-2.511 2.512-6.582.001-9.093-2.511-2.51-6.581-2.51-9.092 0z\"/></svg></a>기능 확인하기</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"typescript\"><pre class=\"language-typescript\"><code class=\"language-typescript\"><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> blog <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">'장태근블로그 devmeeple.github.io'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token function-variable function\">thankYou</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>blogName<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">string</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token builtin\">console</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token interpolation\"><span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">${</span>blogName<span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token string\"> 클릭해주셔서 감사합니다.</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token function\">thankYou</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>blog<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>제거를 마쳤다면, 간단한 프로그램으로 기능을 확인해 보자.</p>\n<p><figure class='gatsby-resp-image-figure' style='margin-bottom: 1rem;'>\n    <span class='gatsby-resp-image-wrapper' style='position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 680px; '>\n      <a class='gatsby-resp-image-link' href='/static/bcc233d7918af05ffd1f90b2598f9691/75f72/thank-you-log.avif' style='display: block' target='_blank' rel='noopener'>\n    <span class='gatsby-resp-image-background-image' style=\"padding-bottom: 14.705882352941178%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/heif;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class='gatsby-resp-image-image' alt='Thank You!' title='' src='/static/bcc233d7918af05ffd1f90b2598f9691/d3231/thank-you-log.avif' srcset='/static/bcc233d7918af05ffd1f90b2598f9691/b521e/thank-you-log.avif 170w,\n/static/bcc233d7918af05ffd1f90b2598f9691/74bf6/thank-you-log.avif 340w,\n/static/bcc233d7918af05ffd1f90b2598f9691/d3231/thank-you-log.avif 680w,\n/static/bcc233d7918af05ffd1f90b2598f9691/78007/thank-you-log.avif 1020w,\n/static/bcc233d7918af05ffd1f90b2598f9691/75f72/thank-you-log.avif 1211w' sizes='(max-width: 680px) 100vw, 680px' style='width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;' loading='lazy' decoding='async'>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class='gatsby-resp-image-figcaption'>Thank You!</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p>업데이트가 성공하고 기능이 정상동작함을 확인할 수 있다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"마치며\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%A7%88%EC%B9%98%EB%A9%B0\" aria-label=\"마치며 permalink\" class=\"heading-anchor before\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M6.188 8.719c.439-.439.926-.801 1.444-1.087 2.887-1.591 6.589-.745 8.445 2.069l-2.246 2.245c-.644-1.469-2.243-2.305-3.834-1.949-.599.134-1.168.433-1.633.898l-4.304 4.306c-1.307 1.307-1.307 3.433 0 4.74 1.307 1.307 3.433 1.307 4.74 0l1.327-1.327c1.207.479 2.501.67 3.779.575l-2.929 2.929c-2.511 2.511-6.582 2.511-9.093 0s-2.511-6.582 0-9.093l4.304-4.306zm6.836-6.836l-2.929 2.929c1.277-.096 2.572.096 3.779.574l1.326-1.326c1.307-1.307 3.433-1.307 4.74 0 1.307 1.307 1.307 3.433 0 4.74l-4.305 4.305c-1.311 1.311-3.44 1.3-4.74 0-.303-.303-.564-.68-.727-1.051l-2.246 2.245c.236.358.481.667.796.982.812.812 1.846 1.417 3.036 1.704 1.542.371 3.194.166 4.613-.617.518-.286 1.005-.648 1.444-1.087l4.304-4.305c2.512-2.511 2.512-6.582.001-9.093-2.511-2.51-6.581-2.51-9.092 0z\"/></svg></a>마치며</h2>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">Volta</code>를 삭제하면 당장의 문제는 해결할 수 있다. 하지만 다양한 버전을 사용하기 위해서 다른 버전 관리자(Node Version Manager)를 고려해야겠다. 우선 급한 대로 <code class=\"language-text\">nvm</code>을 다시 사용 중이다.</p>\n<p><strong>&#x3C;참고 자료></strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.jetbrains.com/ko-kr/idea/whatsnew/\">IntelliJ IDEA 2024.2의 새로운 기능</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://youtrack.jetbrains.com/issue/WEB-67800/Volta-Node-interpreter-version-not-correctly-detected-when-running-Typescript-with-tsx\">YoTrack 'Volta Node interpreter version not correctly detected when running Typescript with\n<code class=\"language-text\">tsx</code>'</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://docs.volta.sh/advanced/uninstall\">VOLTA 'Uninstalling Volta'</a></li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"IntelliJ IDEA Volta 인터프리터 에러 해결하기","date":"August 15, 2024","update":"August 15, 2024","tags":["IDE"],"series":null},"fields":{"slug":"/jetbrains-ideas-volta-error/","readingTime":{"minutes":2.165}}},"seriesList":{"edges":[{"